 "overview": "\u003Cp\u003EBlvd Media Group, LLC (\u0026#8220;BMG\u0026#8221;) develops a FreePlay\u00c2\u00ae Monetizing Methodology, which offers an approach for sites with a virtual economy to increase revenue and content sampling by providing users with a way to earn credits instead of purchasing them.  \u003C/p\u003E\n\n\u003Cp\u003EThe rewardTool\u00c2\u00ae was created to enhance the user experience of completing advertiser offers in exchange for virtual currency.  Using a customizable graphical user interface alongside a \u00e2\u20ac\u0153cover flow\u00e2\u20ac\u009d type ad display created a game-like experience.  A collective intelligence database, multiple layers of fraud protection and total publisher control over advertiser offers create a robust platform for user monetization.\u003C/p\u003E",
